---
import LinkedinIcon from "../components/icons/linkedin.astro";
import GitHubIcon from "../components/icons/github.astro";
---

<section
  id="home"
  class="flex w-full flex-col items-center space-y-6 p-4 py-12 text-justify md:items-start md:p-10 md:py-16 md:text-left lg:py-20"
>
  <h2
    class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl"
  >
    Hola, soy José Rodríguez
  </h2>

  <h1
    id="typed-container"
    class="min-h-[1.2em] text-3xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-blue-500 dark:text-blue-500 sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl"
  >
    <span id="typed"></span>
  </h1>

  <p
    class="w-full max-w-none text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 md:max-w-3xl md:text-2xl"
  >
    Transformo ideas en
    <span class="font-bold text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400"
      >sitios web modernos, rápidos y escalables</span
    >
    para ayudar a marcas y negocios a destacar digitalmente. Construyo cada proyecto
    con
    <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">JavaScript</span>,
    <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Astro</span> y
    <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Tailwind</span>,
    asegurando una experiencia de usuario superior mediante un
    <span class="font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">diseño UI/UX</span>
    funcional.
  </p>

  <nav
    class="flex w-full flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 pt-6 sm:flex-row md:w-auto md:justify-start"
  >
    <a
      href="/assets/CV-Jose-Rodriguez.pdf"
      download="CV-Jose-Rodriguez.pdf"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener"
      class="inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-600 px-8 py-3 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:bg-blue-700 active:scale-95 dark:bg-blue-500 dark:hover:bg-blue-400 sm:w-auto"
    >
      Descargar CV
    </a>

    <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/josergz/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        aria-label="LinkedIn"
        class="transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-110 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400"
      >
        <LinkedinIcon class="size-9 md:size-10" />
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/josergz"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        aria-label="GitHub"
        class="transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-110 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:text-blue-400"
      >
        <GitHubIcon class="size-9 md:size-10" />
      </a>
    </div>
  </nav>
</section>
